n<br />\n唯一一個就係搶番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要得會考<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}